{
  "stem": "3988.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And put that brick on top of it because of rats running around, you know, they shouldn't get into the soup or the leftovers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we put a big stone, you know, on top of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So anyways, that's what we ran into, the cellar.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the cellar was in the back of the house, because we-- the back of the house was a-- like a big square.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the back of the square was the stoves, and like we keep the horses, cows, you know, goats in there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in the back was the cellar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's where we went down there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "A family lived right next door to us too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they had maybe four or five kids.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They came down the basement-- the basement.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was five of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know, we went down the basement, in cellar, and we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, because-- And then we could hear the Germans walking upstairs, you know, in the rooms.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But somehow they didn't go around in the back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Maybe they didn't know, you know, such a thing as a cellar.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We could hear them walking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because if they would, you know, go around the back and see the-- the cellar, and there's people-- because they'll throw down grenades and start shooting, then they probably would have killed us.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Then we stayed there maybe a couple days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then the houses start burning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "When the Germans came in town, they burned down half of the city, you know, start burning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The houses burning next to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You know, and our house was still standing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They didn't burn it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
